::Prowl/FZ/Perndabot::

Prowl watches as FZ slows his decent and lands on the ground. He 
sighs, looking around the battlefield. The CF looked like slag. 
Prowl's eyes narrow as he sees Perndabot standing up, stumbling at 
first, and then heading toward Iron Raptor.

"Arcangel," he says to Angel Prime, still not used to the bot's new 
name, "Can you take care of Zardus for a sec?" (He doesn't know that 
FZ is not Zardus)

Prowl dips downward, flying toward Perndabot with his staff ready to 
strike.
